title: Warriors, Zion Williamson, Jets, and Odell Beckham Jr.
itunes:title: Warriors, Zion Williamson, Jets, and Odell Beckham Jr.
description:
Colin explains how great the Golden State Warriors are, more reasons why F Zion Williamson should want to be traded to the New York Knicks, why the New York Jets fired their GM when they did, and why the New York Giants most likely traded WR Odell Beckham Jr. Guests include Chris Broussard, Mark Schlereth, Cuttino Mobley, and Jason Terry.
